compiledQueryString:
select
  date_trunc('month', order_datetime) as order_month,

  count(*) as number_of_orders,
  sum(sales) as sales_usd0k,
  sum(sales)/count(*) as average_order_value_usd2
from orders

group by 1 
order by 4
